# trovex write-guard zone franche — ONLY these .md STAY real files on disk.
# Everything else routes to the trovex store (trovex_write).
# Owner directive (2026-06-20): full-trovex, EXCEPT blog articles.
#
# Kept on disk for correctness (toolchain / harness / agents read these from
# disk — routing them to the store would break the repo):
README.md
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
LICENSE*
.claude/*
# Shipped skill docs: install.sh + the auto-updater download these from the repo
# into ~/.claude/commands/ + ~/.claude/hooks/ — they MUST stay real files on disk.
skill/**
#
# Blog articles stay publishable source files (they ship as web pages):
**/blog/**
